🔎 Another Common Mistake

Sometimes developers write:

$posts = Post::all();

but use in blade:

{{ $posts->count() }}

Better:

$posts = Post::count();
⚡ Quick Debug Trick

Inside blade write:

{{ dd($posts) }}

If error appears → controller didn't send variable.

